        "authorId" : "73db70fa-89e1-4c46-9a34-73cfc3db7d43",
        "body" : "The macros are closly tied to the implementation details and whenever we change ZIO Mocks, the Mockable macro must be updated aswell, that is why I've moved this into `zio/zio`. We could extract this into seperate subproject though. Since most of `zio-macros` (delegate family) got obsoleted with `ZLayer` and `Has` we are planning to move also `@accessible` into `zio/zio` (maintaining a seperate repository for just one macro feels like too much overhead). I think we can start with `@accessible` and then decide wheather `@Mockable` should be in `tests` or `macros` space.",
